OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FMedical negligence lawyers have urged
OL,8,Fformer patients of the Royal Sussex
OL,9,FCounty Hospital to seek legal advice
OL,10,Fif they believe they may have suffered
OL,11,Fmedical negligence.
OL,13,FThe conduct of staff at the hospital
OL,14,Fin Brighton is currently the focus of
OL,15,Fa Sussex Police investigation,
OL,16,Fcodenamed Operation Bramber,
OL,17,Freportedly examining dozens of cases
OL,18,Fin several departments.
