OL,4,CSussex Hospital patients to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FSlater and Gordon Lawyers held an open-
OL,8,Fdoor legal clinic in Brighton on
OL,9,FFriday, 2 February, for patients and
OL,10,Ffamilies impacted by alleged failings
OL,11,Fin care.
OL,13,FThe firm's head of medical negligence,
OL,14,FEmma Doughty, told ITV News: "This is
OL,15,Fquite an extraordinary case and, in
OL,16,Four experience, it's better to try to
OL,17,Fask people to come forward as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible. The longer things go on, the
OL,19,Fless easy it is for us to investigate."
